57 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE
58 LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA, That we hereby recognize the
59 Founders Day celebration of the Montgomery Alumnae Chapter
60 of Delta Sigma Theta Sorority, Incorporated, honor its
61 esteemed speaker and International President, Cheryl W.
62 Turner, and extend our sincere best wishes for a successful
63 and memorable event.
